Plain window translucency works on 10.6 (WindowServer composites it; only blur is
10.10+). setOpaque:NO + clearColor background, and blit honoring alpha
(premultiply our straight-alpha buffer + kCGImageAlphaPremultipliedLast instead
of the current NoneSkipLast). Opacity = the default-background color's alpha
(contour's opacity config). Same premultiply change the background image needs and
a prerequisite for it.

